headline: Fair Isaac Corporation Announces Date for Reporting of Fourth Quarter Fiscal 2025 Financial Results
summary: BOZEMAN, Mont., October 22, 2025--Global analytics software leader FICO (NYSE: FICO) will announce its fourth quarter fiscal 2025 results on November 5, 2025, after the market closes and will host a conference call on November 5th at 5:00 p.m. Eastern time (4:00 p.m. Central / 2:00 p.m. Pacific).

headline: Fair Isaac's Quarterly Earnings Preview: What You Need to Know
summary: Fair Isaac is scheduled to post its fourth-quarter results soon, and analysts predict a double-digit rise in the company’s bottom-line figure.
